{"id":581117,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【cdtv】两会央视采访-吹牛认真打草稿/","date":"2018-03-19T03:03:03Z","modified":"2018-03-19T03:03:03Z","title":"【CDTV】两会央视采访 吹牛认真打草稿","content":"<p>近日，有网友上传了一段来源媒体不详（疑似外媒）的两会央视采访视频，视频中摄影师捕捉到了中央电视台采访某代表/委员并由一名灰衣女士（疑似记者）手举手写稿件帮忙读稿的镜头，即便如此，这位代表/委员还是自称“紧张”而无法流利读出稿件内容。当拍摄视频的摄影师镜头陆续被两名记者发现后，遭到了躲闪并最终被打断。</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2uykUroiwow?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/changzhanglao/status/975051656671866880</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">吹牛不打草稿是要修炼的。😂</p>\n<p>&mdash; 待处理低端人群 (@RHxzAD9B3zassso) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RHxzAD9B3zassso/status/975007746255966209?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 17, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">哦，原来一本正经的胡说八道就是看着草稿来的，不过这也合情合理；这些鬼话他们自己会信？都是说给傻逼看的，傻逼才坐在新闻联播前信这些。</p>\n<p>&mdash; 维尼大帝 (@RealEmperorPooh) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RealEmperorPooh/status/975070114906361856?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 17, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">那个记者后面的女孩拿着稿子让代表读，这读都读不下去啊!</p>\n<p>&mdash; jim (@leejimca) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/leejimca/status/975055089617526785?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 17, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/JkNtw/status/975151108384370688</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">这人说了真话：马上就完事儿了。</p>\n<p>&mdash; 加满都大人 (@VincentTang116) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VincentTang116/status/975087431170052096?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 17, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/yeuleh/status/975345030016598018</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">说明吹牛是有打草稿滴</p>\n<p>&mdash; 旭 (@minjiangxu) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/minjiangxu/status/975427679900987392?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 18, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">如此低能的人也能當上官，厲害了我的國~</p>\n<p>&mdash; 大澤懷古 (@WheresMyAk47) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WheresMyAk47/status/975131669148643328?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 17, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"ja\" dir=\"ltr\">看看人家多謙虛，吹牛逼前先打好草稿~</p>\n<p>&mdash; 大澤懷古 (@WheresMyAk47) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/WheresMyAk47/status/975132196154593280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 17, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">拍者的角度才是真正的新聞。</p>\n<p>&mdash; Louise Mori (@chaojumori) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/chaojumori/status/975183095035871232?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 18, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13770],"tags":[8974,13344,18604,9149,34146,34145,34144,34147]}